OL,3,CPrestigious warm-up to Wimbledon
OL,4,Ctennis court suffers 'outrageous'
OL,5,Cvandalism
OL,7,FDevonshire Park, the home of the Lexus
OL,8,FEastbourne Open tennis tournament, has
OL,9,Fbeen hit by an "an outrageous act of
OL,10,Fvandalism," the town hall chief has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FCouncil teams arrived early on Friday
OL,14,Fto continue preparations for the grass
OL,15,Fcourt championships which are to begin
OL,16,Fon June 20, only to find extensive
OL,17,Fdamage across several tennis courts.
OL,26,@qD@POUrD@KO]
