OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778951200
OL,3,CPrestigious warm-up to Wimbledon
OL,4,Ctennis court suffers 'outrageous'
OL,5,Cvandalism
OL,7,FStephen Holt, leader of Eastbourne
OL,8,FBorough Council, said: "This is an
OL,9,Foutrageous act of mindless vandalism
OL,10,Fthat shows total disregard for our
OL,11,Ftown, our residents, and the global
OL,12,Fsporting event we are proud to host
OL,13,Feach year."
OL,15,FDevonshire Park is one of Eastbourne's
OL,16,Fgreatest assets, and the council's
OL,17,Fdedicated team have been working
OL,18,Ftirelessly to prepare the courts for
OL,19,Fthe international tournament.
OL,26,@pD@XOUuD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
