PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778951200
OL,3,CPrestigious warm-up to Wimbledon
OL,4,Ctennis court suffers 'outrageous'
OL,5,Cvandalism
OL,7,FFor anyone to deliberately sabotage
OL,8,Fthat work is utterly disgraceful.
OL,10,F"The outdoor tournament, considered as
OL,11,Fa warm-up for the Wimbledon
OL,12,FChampionships which start a week
OL,13,Flater, includes US player Madison
OL,14,FKeys, the 2025 Australian Open winner,
OL,15,Fplus home-favourite Sonay Kartal are
OL,16,Fon the entry list.
OL,18,FKeys ` who won the title in 2014 and
OL,19,F2023 ` is returning to the south coast
OL,20,Fin a bid to complete a hat-trick of
OL,21,Ftitles at Eastbourne.
OL,26,@rD@AO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
