CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778951200
OL,3,CPrestigious warm-up to Wimbledon
OL,4,Ctennis court suffers 'outrageous'
OL,5,Cvandalism
OL,7,FSecurity measures are being bolstered
OL,8,Fby the council in response to the
OL,9,Fdamage.
OL,11,FMr Holt said town hall chiefs are
OL,12,Fworking closely with Sussex Police and
OL,13,FCCTV footage from the site and
OL,14,Fsurrounding area is being scoured.
OL,16,FHe described the damage as a "setback"
OL,17,Fbut said efforts are being made to
OL,18,Fensure the venue is ready in time to
OL,19,Fstage the tournament.
OL,26,@xD@^OUxD@fO]
