PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778951200
OL,3,CPrestigious warm-up to Wimbledon
OL,4,Ctennis court suffers 'outrageous'
OL,5,Cvandalism
OL,7,FMr Holt added: "We will do everything
OL,8,Fpossible to support the police in
OL,9,Fidentifying those responsible ` it is
OL,10,Fcriminal damage that could have
OL,11,Fdisrupted a major sporting event.
OL,13,F"However, despite this setback our
OL,14,Fbrilliant team at Devonshire Park are
OL,15,Fworking to ensure the courts are
OL,16,Fhanded over to the LTA (Lawn Tennis
OL,17,FAssociation), ready for the world
OL,18,Fclass tennis that we're all looking
OL,19,Fforward to."
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@AOU{D@LO]
